Body: I got one of those phone boosters for Android but it looks like it does not work very well because when I run a clean it stops at 88% or somewhere and immediately tells me that I have to clean again.I figured that it is some kind of bug or that an app is using a lot of RAM and it can't be cleaned.Is there a way to clean more RAM so my phone can get faster?
